title: KMSAuto Net 2014 1.2.8 Portable [Ru/UA]
description:
KMSAuto Net 2014 1.2.8 Portable [Ru/UA] 
Interface language- Russian, Ukrainian
Activation of Windows Vista, 7, 8, 8.1, Server 2008, 2008 R2, 2012, 2012 R2 and Office 2010, 2013 VL edition. Additionaly activates: Windows 8.1 Single Language; Windows 8.1 Core; Windows 8.1 Core N; Windows 8.1 Pro WMC; Windows Embedded 8.1 Industry Pro; Windows Server 2012 R2 Standard; Windows Server 2012 R2 Datacenter. Requires .NET Framework 4.5.
